Architecture: all
Depends: python-mysqldb, ezweb-platform-common (= ${Source-Version})
Suggests: mysql-server-5.0 | mysql-server-5.1 | mysql-server
Description: MySQL suport for EzWeb Platform
 EzWeb Platform, the MORFEO Open Source Community Mashup Platform, provides you
 a framework for building modern enterprise and personal mashups following the
 main Web 2.0 ideas.
 .
 This package provides common files for supporting EzWeb Platform instances
 using MySQL as DBMS.

Package: ezweb-platform-sqlite3
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python-pysqlite2, ezweb-platform-common (= ${Source-Version})
Description: SQLite3 suport for EzWeb Platform
 EzWeb Platform, the MORFEO Open Source Community Mashup Platform, provides you
 a framework for building modern enterprise and personal mashups following the
 main Web 2.0 ideas.
 .
 This package provides common files for supporting EzWeb Platform instances
 using SQLite3 as database engine.
